@Toc "Main"

Quitting FFRStatus task.
************************

     You can quit FFRS_Status by

   @{b}*@{ub} Double-clicking on its icon again

   @{b}*@{ub} Typing FFRS_Status in a CLI or Shell

   @{b}*@{ub} Sending it a CTRL-C


@EndNode

